Python 安裝
環境python 2.7
	
# 套件安裝: http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/#pysparse
- pip(安裝套件的套件):
1.	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pypa/pip/master/contrib/get-pip.py
2.	執行1.下載的內容: python get-pip.py
3.	套件檢查: pip list
# IDE選擇:
1.	pip install jupyter(啟動指令jupyter notebook)
2.	eclipse 套件 pydev
# 爬蟲套件:
- pip install request
- pip install beautifulsoup4
- pip install jieba (中文分詞: http://blog.fukuball.com/ru-he-shi-yong-jieba-jie-ba-zhong-wen-fen-ci-cheng-shi/)
- pip install scikit-learn 
# 動態網頁: Google Analytics GA
- https://sofree.cc/ga-demographics-interests/
- http://www.yesharris.com/category/google-analytics-basic/

